messages.message: It's like flashcards that remind you based on getting it wrong or right. Pretty awesome if you have something new trainees need to memorize I can add it to the app easily to study.
Wow, the job requirements describe me perfectly. Can I call someone next Monday to talk about this? I am in class all of this week from 7am to 7pm.
I would love to catch up today.  Is 3:00 ok?  California and Arizona are on the same timezone right?
